ed="T" n="0833a07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0833a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000010777"><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0833001"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0833001"/>州</placeName><placeName>西靈塔寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A001894">懷信</persName><ptr target="#n2506"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0833a08"/><persName key="A001894">釋懷信</persName>者，居處<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName>，別無奇迹。<date from-iso="+0843-02-07" key="j20289972029351" to-iso="+0844-01-27"><name>會昌</name>三年<lb
ed="T" n="0833a09"/>癸亥歲</date><ptr target="#n2507"/>，<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>為<persName key="A012399">趙歸真</persName>排毀<name>釋</name>門，將欲堙<lb
ed="T" n="0833a10"/>滅教法。有<placeName key="PL000000010798">淮南</placeName>詞客<persName key="A012402">劉隱之</persName>薄遊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g674"/><placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>，旅<lb
ed="T" n="0833a11"/>泊之宵，夢中如泛海焉。迴顧見塔一所，東<lb
ed="T" n="0833a12"/>度見是<placeName key="PL000000010777"><placeName>淮南</placeName><placeName>西靈寺塔</placeName></placeName>。<ref type="person" target="#PL000000010777">其塔</ref>峻峙，制度校<persName key="A002046">胡<lb
ed="T" n="0833a13"/>太后</persName><placeName key="PL000000023866">永寧塔</placeName>少分耳<ptr target="#n2508"/>。<ref type="person" target="#PL000000010777">其塔</ref>第三層，見<persName key="A001894">信</persName>凭欄<lb
ed="T" n="0833a14"/>與<persName key="A012402">隱之</persName>交談，且曰：「暫送塔過<placeName key="PL000000000151">東海</placeName>，旬日而<lb
ed="T" n="0833a15"/>還。」數日，<persName key="A012402">隱之</persName>歸<placeName key="PL000000010783"><anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz2"/>揚州<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz2"/></placeName>，即往謁<persName key="A001894">信</persName>。<persName key="A001894">信</persName>曰：「記得<lb
ed="T" n="0833a16"/>海上相見時否？」<persName key="A012402">隱之</persName>了然省悟。後數日天火，<lb
ed="T" n="0833a17"/>焚塔俱盡──白雨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1709"/>傾澍，傍有草堂，一無所<lb
ed="T" n="0833a18"/>損。由是觀之，<placeName key="PL000000000151">東海</placeName>人見<placeName key="PL000000023866">永寧塔</placeName>不謬矣<ptr target="#n2516"/>。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0833a1901"><lb
ed="T" n="0833a19"/>系曰：塔焚皆云往<placeName key="PL000000000151">東海</placeName>，海豈納煨燼耶？通<lb
ed="T" n="0833a20"/>曰：「五行為物亦七大性<ptr target="#n2509"/>，可弗周遍法界乎？<lb
ed="T" n="0833a21"/>順則相生，逆則相害。雖逆順各時，與法界<lb
ed="T" n="0833a22"/>同其分齊，證知唯有『識』耳。且天仙鬼物與人<lb
ed="T" n="0833a23"/>相反：殊勝諸天則定果宮殿<ptr target="#n2510"/>，神仙則附物變<lb
ed="T" n="0833a24"/>化<ptr target="#n2511"/>，鬼神則歆其食氣<ptr target="#n2512"/>──質礙之流，火化則得受<lb
ed="T" n="0833a25"/>用也。凡塔剎嚴麗，多被鬼神取旃<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1050"/>。海若川<lb
ed="T" n="0833a26"/>侯<ptr target="#n2513"/>，亦非人也，如<placeName key="PL000000008619"><placeName>陳</placeName><placeName>重雲殿</placeName></placeName>天火焚，<placeName key="PL000000000151">東海</placeName>人時<lb
ed="T" n="0833a27"/>見殿影焉<ptr target="#n2514"/>。又近<persName key="A011960">馬<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>霸<placeName key="PL000000028665">湖南</placeName>，末年<placeName key="PL000000059031"><anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz3"/>天<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz3"/>冊閣</placeName><ptr target="#n2515"/><lb
ed="T" n="0833a28"/>為<anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz5"/>天<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz5"/>火焚，<placeName key="PL000000029413">朗州</placeName>守此夜聞空中呵喝言『迴<lb
ed="T" n="0833a29"/>避，<name><anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz7"/>天<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz7"/>冊閣</name>來也。』雲中騰沸，若千萬人<anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz9"/>舁<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz9"/>荷重<pb ed="T" n="0833b" xml:id="T50.2061.0833b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0833b01"/>物然，累日，方<placeName key="PL000000028665">潭州</placeName>火矣。若<persName key="A001894">懷信</persName>見<persName key="A012402">劉隱之</persName>夢，<lb
ed="T" n="0833b02"/><persName key="A001894">信</persName>亦不可測之僧也。」</p>
